What you need to know:  Chinhoi, who has dominated the Tour over the past three years, shot two under par 70, to lead by one shot from Muthaiga’s Greg Snow who shot one under par 71The top two were followed closely by a group of five other players on level par 72The event got underway after the Pro-Am held on Saturday where the team of Royal Nairobi Golf Club pro Hesbon Kutwa and his amateurs Sanish Chadha, Sameer Nanji and Sameer Kassam posted a total of 90 points including the pro’s 37